                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="p-1">
                        Add <code class="text-bold text-primary">data-js="dropdown"</code> to the button and set
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">data-target</code> to the menu ID.
                        The script opens or closes the dropdown and updates
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">aria-expanded</code> automatically.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </article>

