                </div>
                <div class="card-body">
                    <p class="p-1">
                        Add position classes directly on the <code class="text-bold text-primary">.dropdown-menu</code> to control where it appears.
                        If no position class is added, the menu defaults to
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.bottom</code> and
                        <code class="text-bold text-primary">.left</code>.
                    </p>

